description:
PDF Editor OCR Plug-in 

 Turn scanned PDFs into fully selectable, searchable, and editable files. After enabling the OCR Plug-in on Wondershare PDF Editor, all features in PDF Editor will be applicable to scanned PDFs, such as: 
 - Copy text and images from scanned PDF 
 - Edit scanned PDF texts, images, and pages 
 - Convert scanned PDFs to word, PowerPoint, Excel, HTML, EPUB, etc.

Key Benefits: 
 - Recognize text from scanned, image-based PDF files. 
 - Enable you to search text within the scanned PDF files. 
 - Let you copy text and images from scanned PDF files. 
 - Empower you to edit scanned PDFs on Wondershare PDF Editor. 
 - Support multiple languages.
